It is possible to prepare CSS Stylesheets and JavaScript Sources as a content nodes. At the top of *Content* tab there
is a button *New Content* that offers a list of available content types to be created. Select the type "CSS Stylesheets"
or "JavaScript Sources" and press "Create" button. The simple content editor should be shown to the user.

